  {
    "content_id": 694158,
    "reference_id": 13955,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神的神能已將（字面意思是<em>祂的神能已經</em>）：神的名字並未出現在希臘文文本中；彼得指的可能是「我們的主耶穌」的<em>神能</em>（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:2\">1:2</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:3",
          "end_ref": "61001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694157,
    "reference_id": 13954,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:3–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001003-61001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神在基督裡賜給我們這一切的說明（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:3-2Pet1:4\">1:3–4</a>），構成了一個迫切地勸勉的基礎，敦促人們要在對基督的認識上長進（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:11\">1:5–11</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:3",
          "end_ref": "61001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694159,
    "reference_id": 13956,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>就得與神的性情有分：彼得的意思可能不是我們的靈與神合而為一，而是信徒享有神的特質（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44\">利11:44</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:43-Matt5:48\">太5:43–48</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:24\">弗4:24</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1\">5:1</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:4",
          "end_ref": "61001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694160,
    "reference_id": 13957,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:5–7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001005-61001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這些經文的階梯式結構中，每個美德會帶出另一個美德，這是一種常見的文學手法，稱為堆垛（<em>sorites</em>；譯註：即一系列<span>循序漸進的陳述</span>）。這類經文中的順序並不是重點——例如，彼得並不是在強調德行必須先於知識。然而，愛是美德的頂峰（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:7\">1:7</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:5",
          "end_ref": "61001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694149,
    "reference_id": 13946,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>弟兄們：這個希臘文單詞（adelphoi）指的是同一家族的男性和女性成員。</p></li><li><p>應當更加殷勤，使……（字面意思是<em>要熱心，以確保</em>）：彼得並不是說我們蒙神揀選得救是取決於我們的行為，而是說我們在基督徒美德上熱切成長的態度證實了我們確實是被神揀選的。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:10",
          "end_ref": "61001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694150,
    "reference_id": 13947,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:12–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001012-61001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>彼得是在他生命的<span>晚年</span>寫下這封書信，彼得後書的風格與於一種流行的猶太文學類型——<em>遺訓（testament）</em>——相似；在遺訓這個類型中，年長且受人尊敬的領袖在臨終時會給予他的孩子或其他人最後的教導（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:1-Deut33:29\">申31–33</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:1-Josh24:33\">書24</a>）。這個文學類型最著名的例子之一，是猶太著作<em>十二族長遺訓</em>（<em>The Testaments of the Twelve</em>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:12",
          "end_ref": "61001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694151,
    "reference_id": 13948,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這個預言可能是來自於一個異象，但更有可能的是彼得在回想耶穌對他的死的預言（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:18-John21:19\">約21:18–19</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:14",
          "end_ref": "61001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694152,
    "reference_id": 13949,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:16–18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001016-61001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>乖巧捏造的虛言（字面意思是<em>巧妙編造的神話</em>）：那些假教師可能是在指控基督再來的信息只是一個啟發性的寓言，並不是真實的事實。</p></li><li><p>乃是親眼見過他的威榮：耶穌變相（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:1-Matt17:9\">太17:1–9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:2-Mark9:8\">可9:2–8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:28-Luke9:36\">路9:28–36</a>）顯明了耶穌是榮耀的王，預示了基督的再來。彼得的信心不是基於人的推測，而是基於親眼見證的經歷。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:16",
          "end_ref": "61001018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694153,
    "reference_id": 13950,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:16–21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001016-61001021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>彼得對假教師的譴責（第<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:22\">2</a>章）是以耶穌確定會再來的這個教導為框架（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:1-2Pet3:13\">3:1–13</a>）。假教師可能否認基督再來和審判的真實性。而彼得親眼見證的經歷（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16-2Pet1:18\">1:16–18</a>）和聖經預言的內在可靠性（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19-2Pet1:21\">1:19–21</a>），使基督的再來成為必然的事實。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:16",
          "end_ref": "61001021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694154,
    "reference_id": 13951,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>天這個詞在某些譯本中是以首字母大寫來呈現（Day），因為這是<em>耶和華的日子</em>的簡寫，指的是神介入歷史拯救祂的百姓並審判仇敵的時刻（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:4-Isa13:12\">賽13:4–12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:1-Joel2:32\">珥2:1–32</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:1-Zeph2:3\">番2:1–3</a>）。基督的第一次臨到<span>表示主拯救祂子民的時代的開始</span>。而耶和華審判仇敵的將來的日子尚未臨到。</p></li><li><p>晨星：金星，即「晨星」，通常會在黎明前出現在東方的地平線上。彼得顛倒了自然事件的順序：耶和華的日子的開端，帶來晨星在信徒心裡發光。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:19",
          "end_ref": "61001019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694156,
    "reference_id": 13953,
    "title": "彼得後書 1:20–21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001020-61001021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>隨私意解說（或<em>是關乎個人解釋的問題</em>）：<span>重點很可能是先知們並非是獨自解讀神所賜給他們的異象。</span>神使先知清楚明白其意義，以便他們能夠清楚且可靠地發預言。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61001020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:20",
          "end_ref": "61001021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 1:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694171,
    "reference_id": 13968,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>他們（譯註：和合本未譯出此代名詞）：彼得在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:3\">二章1至3節</a>中使用未來時態並不是表示假先知尚未出現，而是指耶穌所說關於假教師會出現的預言（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:11\">太24:11</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">24</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:22\">可13:22</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:29-Acts20:31\">徒20:29–31</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:6\">提後3:1–6</a>）。假教師已經出現並成就了那個預言。</p></li><li><p>連買他們的主他們也不承認：假教師可能公開否認基督，但更有可能的是，他們不道德的行為被視為否認基督（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:16\">多1:16</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:1",
          "end_ref": "61002001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694161,
    "reference_id": 13958,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:1–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002001-61002003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>總會有假先知會在真先知（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:20-2Pet1:21\">1:20–21</a>）身邊，這些假先知必受到神的審判。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:1",
          "end_ref": "61002003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694174,
    "reference_id": 13971,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>錯誤的教導最悲哀的影響之一是真道會被旁觀的世人抵毀。由於假教師們不道德和貪婪的行為，他們使基督蒙羞。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:2",
          "end_ref": "61002002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694176,
    "reference_id": 13973,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>審判的第一個例子是犯罪的天使：廣泛的猶太傳統認為，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:1-Gen6:5\">創世記六章1至5節</a>中的「神的兒子們」（被理解為天使）與女人發生了關係，因此在那時被神審判（見<em>以諾一書</em>〔<em>1&nbsp;Enoch</em>〕6–10；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:19-1Pet3:20\">彼前3:19–20</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:6\">猶1:6</a>）。</p></li><li><p>交在黑暗坑中：對陰間世界的這種描述在古代世界中頗為常見，這可能是隱喻性的說法。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:4",
          "end_ref": "61002004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694175,
    "reference_id": 13972,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:4–10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002004-61002010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>舊約聖經中的三個審判例子表明，神會為那些對祂忠誠的人伸冤，並會審判那些拒絕祂的人，包括那些假教師（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:3\">2:3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:4",
          "end_ref": "61002010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694177,
    "reference_id": 13974,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>第二個審判的例子是，神在挪亞的時代並沒有寬容那古代的世界。在洪水中，神毀滅了除了挪亞和他一家之外所有人的性命（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:1-Gen8:22\">創6–8章</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:5",
          "end_ref": "61002005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694178,
    "reference_id": 13975,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>第三個審判的例子是神審判了所多瑪和蛾摩拉兩座城市。這些城裡的人們極不道德，以至於神從天上降下硫磺毀滅他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24\">創19:24</a>）。彼得則關注這一行動的結果：這些城變成了灰燼。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:6",
          "end_ref": "61002006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694179,
    "reference_id": 13976,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:7–8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002007-61002008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>雖然舊約聖經中並未將羅得描繪成特別公義的人（見「<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203399\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesProfiles\">羅得</span>」簡介），但他基本上仍然忠於耶和華；猶太傳統也將他描繪為義人（見<em>所羅門智訓</em>〔<em>Wisdom of Solomon</em>〕10:6，19:17）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:7",
          "end_ref": "61002008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 203399,
          "content_id": 650815,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotesProfiles",
          "label": "羅得",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694180,
    "reference_id": 13977,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>主知道搭救敬虔的人脫離試探：如同挪亞的家人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:5\">2:5</a>）和羅得（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:7\">2:7</a>）所<span>顯明的</span>，耶和華對自己的百姓是信實的。彼得的讀者需要確信，他們在面對假的教導和世人的<span>譏誚</span>時竭力活出敬虔生活的努力，必會得到獎賞。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:9",
          "end_ref": "61002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694163,
    "reference_id": 13960,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:10a",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>污穢的情慾：這指的通常是不合情理的性慾，可能是特別指同性戀（參所多瑪和蛾摩拉，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:6\">2:6</a>）。</p></li><li><p>假教師相當傲慢，以至於他們拒絕聽從任何權威，只聽自己。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:10",
          "end_ref": "61002010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694164,
    "reference_id": 13961,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:10b",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在尊位的：這可能是指墮落的天使，與<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:11\">二章11節</a>中所說的天使形成對比。即使<span>譏笑</span>墮落的天使也是錯的，因為他們帶有那榮耀起源的印記——他們擁有真正的能力，對人構成真實的威脅。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:10",
          "end_ref": "61002010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694162,
    "reference_id": 13959,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:10–16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002010-61002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>對這些假教師的描述更側重於他們生活的方式，而非他們所教導的內容。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:10",
          "end_ref": "61002016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694165,
    "reference_id": 13962,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>就是天使……還不用毀謗的話在主面前告他們，但那些假教師非常膽大任性，毫不猶豫地如此行。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:11",
          "end_ref": "61002011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694166,
    "reference_id": 13963,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>正與你們一同坐席，就以自己的詭詐為快樂：參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:12\">猶大書一章12節</a>。基督徒經常一起團契吃飯來敬拜紀念主（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46\">徒2:46</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1\">6:1</a>）。假教師利用這些團契吃飯的時間來欺騙真信徒。有些抄本的讀法是<em>他們在與你們一起團契吃飯的時候尋找樂趣</em>（或<em>狂歡，</em>或<em>暢飲</em>）<em>。</em>如果這種讀法是正確的，那他們就是在利用團契吃飯的時間來放縱自我（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:20-1Cor11:22\">林前11:20–22</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:13",
          "end_ref": "61002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694167,
    "reference_id": 13964,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>巴蘭就是那貪愛不義之工價的先知：儘管已經求問神他應該怎麼做，但巴蘭還是決心走自己的路，希望能得到巴勒的錢財（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:1-Num24:25\">民22–24章</a>）。舊約聖經的記載暗示了巴蘭的貪婪，而猶太傳統進一步發展了這一主題（見<em>民數記拉巴</em>〔<em>Numbers Rabbah</em>〕20:10；<em>米示拿 先賢集</em>〔<em>Mishnah Avot</em>〕5:22；斐羅，<em>摩西</em> 〔Philo, <em>Moses</em>〕1:266–268）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:15",
          "end_ref": "61002015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694168,
    "reference_id": 13965,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:17–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002017-61002022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>彼得繼續他對假教師的描述，並解釋他們對其他人的影響。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:17",
          "end_ref": "61002022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694169,
    "reference_id": 13966,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>那些剛才脫離妄行的人：假教師巧妙地針對剛信主的人，也就是那些才剛委身於基督的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:18",
          "end_ref": "61002018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694170,
    "reference_id": 13967,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>歷世歷代以來，虛假的教導的誘惑之一，就是在於承諾<span>能使人脫離權柄得自由</span>，但這種自由是虛幻的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:16\">羅6:16</a>）。假教師雖然沉浸在他們脫離權柄而得的自由中（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:10\">彼後2:10</a>），但實際上卻仍是罪和敗壞的奴僕。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:19",
          "end_ref": "61002019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694172,
    "reference_id": 13969,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>他們末後的景況就比先前更不好了：那些假教師或他們的追隨者曾經知道真理，但他們故意拒絕真理，使得他們的處境比無知地生活在罪中時更為糟糕。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:20",
          "end_ref": "61002020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694173,
    "reference_id": 13970,
    "title": "彼得後書 2:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61002022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>「狗所吐的，牠轉過來又吃」：人們並不認為狗是友好的家庭寵物，而認為是野生且骯髒的獸類。</p></li><li><p>「豬洗淨了又回到泥裏去滾」：這句俗語可能出自約公元前500年流行的一本語錄，名為阿希卡（<em>Ahiqar</em>），其中寫道：「我兒啊，對我而言，你就像那頭與高貴之人一起洗浴的豬，牠從浴池中出來後，一看到骯髒的坑，就下去在裡面打滾」（<em>阿希卡</em>〔<em>Ahiqar</em>〕8:18）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61002022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:22",
          "end_ref": "61002022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 2:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694188,
    "reference_id": 13985,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>我現在寫給你們的是第二封信：第一封信可能是彼得前書。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:1",
          "end_ref": "61003001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694181,
    "reference_id": 13978,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:1–13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003001-61003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>彼得從譴責假教師轉向勸勉信徒。那些假教師懷疑基督的再來，而這需要明確的教導來應對。基督徒應持守使徒所傳關於審判之日的信息，並在對那一日的期待中過敬虔的生活。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:1",
          "end_ref": "61003013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694189,
    "reference_id": 13986,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>舊約聖經中的聖先知們預言了主的日子，那時神會審判祂的仇敵（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"13951\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">1:19的研讀註釋</span>）。</p></li><li><p>主救主的命令：耶穌已經透過使徒教導教會。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:2",
          "end_ref": "61003002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 13951,
          "content_id": 694154,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "彼得後書 1:19",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694190,
    "reference_id": 13987,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>末世：彼得不僅僅是預言未來的事件；他也論及他的讀者當下的情形。在新約聖經中，<em>末世</em>指的是耶穌第一次來臨與他第二次來臨之間的時期（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17\">徒2:17</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">來1:2</a>）。這是神的應許成就的時候。</p></li><li><p>必有好譏誚的人：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:22\">箴言一章22節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:7-Prov9:8\">九章7至8節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:1\">十三章1節</a>。好譏誚的人不使用證據和邏輯來辯論，而是貶低和嘲笑真理。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:3",
          "end_ref": "61003003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694191,
    "reference_id": 13988,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>從列祖睡了以來：那些假教師可能會聲稱，儘管神應許會介入歷史，但事情並沒有真正改變，也永遠不會改變。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:4",
          "end_ref": "61003004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694192,
    "reference_id": 13989,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>創造是顯明假教師的錯誤的第一個證據：變化確實會發生。若神創造了世界，那麼祂當然也可以毀滅它。</p></li><li><p>從水而出、藉水而成的地：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">創世記一章2節</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:6-Gen1:10\">6至10節</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:5",
          "end_ref": "61003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694193,
    "reference_id": 13990,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>舊約聖經將火與耶和華的日子聯想在一起（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:30\">賽30:30</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:15-Isa66:16\">66:15–16</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:7",
          "end_ref": "61003007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694194,
    "reference_id": 13991,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>彼得間接提及<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:4\">詩篇九十篇4節</a>。神按照祂的時間尺度作工。祂會在祂認為合適的時候派遣祂的使者。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:8",
          "end_ref": "61003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694182,
    "reference_id": 13979,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>形質本身指的可能是有形宇宙的基本構成，或指太陽、月亮和星星。</p></li><li><p>都要燒盡了：此處的希臘文很難理解；有些譯本的讀法可能是表示所有受造物在審判的時候，<em>將要在神面前顯現</em>，且神認為其應受審判。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:10",
          "end_ref": "61003010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694183,
    "reference_id": 13980,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>切切仰望神的日子來到：神的百姓可以透過他們的悔改和敬虔的生活加速末世的來臨（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19-Acts3:20\">徒3:19–20</a>）。</p></li><li><p>有形質的都要被烈火鎔化：參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:3-Mic1:4\">彌迦書一章3至4節</a>；另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:19-Isa64:1\">以賽亞書63章19節至六十四章1節</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:12",
          "end_ref": "61003012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694184,
    "reference_id": 13981,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>新天新地：見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">以賽亞書六十五章17節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:22\">六十六章22節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:27\">啟示錄二十一章</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:13",
          "end_ref": "61003013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694185,
    "reference_id": 13982,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>我們所親愛的兄弟保羅：新約聖經對彼得和保羅之間的關係描述不多。由於在安提阿的爭論（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11-Gal2:14\">加2:11–14</a>），有時人們認為兩人彼此敵對，但新約聖經描繪了一幅不同的景像。彼得和保羅對於傳給外邦人福音基本上持相同意見（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:2-Acts11:18\">徒11:2–18</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:7-Acts15:11\">15:7–11</a>）。西拉和馬可是保羅和彼得的同工（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:12-1Pet5:13\">彼前5:12–13</a>）。根據傳統，兩位使徒在公元60年代中期，在尼祿的逼迫中於羅馬殉道。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "61003015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:15",
          "end_ref": "61003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2PE 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 694186,
    "reference_id": 13983,
    "title": "彼得後書 3:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>彼得在這個時候可能已經知道除了其中一兩封以外的保羅所有的書信。彼得的話暗示著他認為保羅的書信屬於聖經的範疇。</p>",
